Title: Fixed editing of views using the "Downtime for host/service" sorter or column
Level: 1
Component: multisite
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.2.6b1
Date: 1417449307
Class: fix

Views which were using the "Downtime for host/service" (downtime_what) sorter or column
were loosing this information when opening the view for editing and saving it again.
